                             <desc>
                                The portion of manuscript <locus from="1" to="88"/> is a palimpsest. It originally hosted a <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2701Dawit">Psalter</ref>,
                                written horizontally in a <date>15th-century</date> hand. The title of Psalm 5 and the number of lines of Psalm 4 are legible in red ink on <locus target="#5"/>.
